                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial-footer">
                        <span class="badge bg-success">Urgence niveau 2</span>
                        <span class="text-muted">Temps d'attente: 12 min</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="testimonial-card">
                    <div class="testimonial-header">
                        <div class="patient-avatar">
                            <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=2" alt="Patient">
                        </div>
                        <div class="patient-info">
                            <h5>Jean Martin</h5>
                            <div class="patient-rating">
                                <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                <i class="bi bi-star-half"></i>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-date">
                            <small>Il y a 1 semaine</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial-body">
                        <p>
                            "Le système digitalisé facilite énormément la prise en charge.
                            Moins de paperasse, plus d'efficacité. Bravo pour cette innovation au service des patients."
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial-footer">
                        <span class="badge bg-warning">Urgence niveau 3</span>
                        <span class="text-muted">Temps d'attente: 25 min</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section FAQ améliorée -->
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2 class="section-title">
                <i class="bi bi-question-circle"></i>
                Questions fréquentes
            </h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Toutes les réponses à vos questions</p>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="faq-search mb-4">
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <span class="input-group-text">
                            <i class="bi bi-search"></i>
                        </span>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Rechercher une question..." id="faqSearch">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-categories mb-4">
                    <div class="category-tags">
                        <button class="category-tag active" data-category="all">Toutes</button>
                        <button class="category-tag" data-category="triage">Triage</button>
                        <button class="category-tag" data-category="waiting">Temps d'attente</button>
                        <button class="category-tag" data-category="documents">Documents</button>
                        <button class="category-tag" data-category="emergency">Urgences</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

